<section class="hero">
  <h1>Wait, or <em>Deploy Now?</em></h1>
  <div class="hero-subtitle">Sometimes waiting for a better Bitcoin entry pays off &mdash; and the channel tells you when.</div>
  <p class="subtitle">The third of the trilogy: where the others ask <em>how</em> to deploy, this one asks <em>whether</em> &mdash; is today&rsquo;s position one where waiting <em>or</em> deploying decisively becomes the prudent call?</p>
</section>

